name: BUSH'S BEST 16 oz Canned Black Refried Beans, Source of Plant Based Protein and Fiber, Low Fat, Gluten Free, (Pack of 12)
short_description: CANNED BLACK REFRIED BEANS: Our Refried Beans complement any dish—fajitas, empanadas, chicken and rice, dips and more—or stand alone as a family favorite
product_description: Looking for all of the traditional, rich flavors that make black beans the key ingredient in a wide variety of popular Cuban, Mexican and Puerto Rican dishes? BUSH’S ® Refried Black Beans have them in spades. Cooked to the perfect texture and seasoned to perfection, our beans complement any dish—fajitas, empanadas, chicken and rice, dips and more—or stand alone as a family favorite. For more than 110 years, BUSH’S® has been dedicated to bringing our best to kitchens, cookouts and gatherings of family and friends across the country. We’ve grown from a small tomato cannery into the best-known name in beans, with a wide range of delicious products, flavors and, of course, our Secret Family Recipe. Along the way, we’ve remained independent, family owned and uncompromising in our commitment to quality, community and doing business the right way. We believe that our founder A.J. Bush would be proud of the company we are today — and even prouder to share our full line of great-tasting bean products with you. Visit bushbeans.com/recipes for recipe inspiration and more.

name: Organic Dried Black Beans 5 lb, Unsalted, Low-Sodium, Non-GMO, Farmed From Regenerative Soil, Tested Clean Certified – Rich in Fiber & Protein – Perfect for Soups, Burritos, Salads & Chili by Doudlah Farms
short_description: 🌱Quality Beans: Our Black Beans are tested free from 220 chemicals, Glyphosate, and AMPA. We believe in wholesome, nutrient-dense, rich, safe foods—farmed right. Our black beans are Certified Organic, non-GMO, Gluten-Free, and without Artificial Flavors or Preservatives.

🌱100% American Farmer Grown: Locally grown and packaged in Wisconsin, we are a sixth-generation farm family that cares about the planet and the next generation. Your purchase directly supports our food practices and a healthy rural farm economy.

🌱Taste Profile: Rich, earthy flavor with subtle sweetness. When cooked, they develop a creamy texture with a deep, savory taste. Perfect for soups, stews, salads, and Latin American dishes like black bean soup or feijoada. Versatile and full of flavor!

🌱Regenerative Farming: Your health is deeply rooted in our soils. We continuously test our crops for nutrient-richness throughout the growing process, ensuring tested clean beans, free from harmful residues. By replenishing & nourishing our soil, we’re able to provide you with the healthiest possible plant-based proteins.

🌱Our Why: Our dad passed away from Midwest Farmer's Cancer in 2011. Since then, we have been committed to gradually transitioning our conventional farm to 100% organic, using biodynamic and regenerative farming practices. This approach ensures freshness, purity, and health for you and your loved ones
